# | color0  | bright white   |
# | color1  | bright red     |
# | color2  | bright green   |
# | color3  | bright yellow  |
# | color4  | bright blue    |
# | color5  | bright magenta |
# | color6  | bright cyan    |
# | color7  | bright black   |
